<p>how to create routing for custom 403 error page for a s3 bucket? below have given the routing i tried. 403.html is public. all other objects in bucket is private. do i need to make bucket as well public?</p>  <pre><code>&lt;RoutingRules&gt; &lt;RoutingRule&gt; &lt;Condition&gt;   &lt;HttpErrorCodeReturnedEquals&gt;403&lt;/HttpErrorCodeReturnedEquals&gt; &lt;/Condition&gt; &lt;Redirect&gt;   &lt;ReplaceKeyWith&gt;403.html&lt;/ReplaceKeyWith&gt;   &lt;HttpRedirectCode&gt;302&lt;/HttpRedirectCode&gt; &lt;/Redirect&gt; &lt;/RoutingRule&gt; &lt;/RoutingRules&gt; </code></pre>